{"lastModified":null,"uri":"c::10549594650::vessel::320853c0-f03a-11ee-848f-314e75eb0e80","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Summer Operating Area: Greece, Canary Islands\nWinter Operating Area: Leeward Islands, Windward Islands\n\nWelcome aboard this amazing catamaran, Avel Vaez, a Marsaudon ORC 57. Avel Vaez is definitely a catamaran for the more adventurous at heart or for those looking for a true sailing adventure. Built for speed and performance, this sailing vessel will not only get you from A to B quickly, but also comfortably. Designed by Marc Lombard, who also designs for Nautitech and Privilege, Avel Vaez has plenty of living space but has been optimized for weight reduction.\n\nThe entire boat is elegantly finished that can only be describes as “industrial chic” with luxury touches. With a spacious cockpit and saloon offering panoramic views, guests can enjoy their sporty sailing vacation is style and comfort. Stepping down into the hulls, guests will find the theme “keep it light” flows into the layout of the 4 airy double cabins with 2 heads.\n\nFast sailing the Caribbean on Avel Vaez will exhilarate any sailing enthusiast that steps aboard.","blueprint":{"name":"AVEL VAEZ","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::320853c0-f03a-11ee-848f-314e75eb0e80::assets::46738480-2826-11f1-87e8-fd43b6a5a5b5/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::320853c0-f03a-11ee-848f-314e75eb0e80::assets::46727311-2826-11f1-851d-1baf5e6aaf43/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::320853c0-f03a-11ee-848f-314e75eb0e80::assets::46735d70-2826-11f1-851d-1baf5e6aaf43/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::320853c0-f03a-11ee-848f-314e75eb0e80::assets::4672e840-2826-11f1-87e7-fd43b6a5a5b5/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::320853c0-f03a-11ee-848f-314e75eb0e80::assets::46746ee0-2826-11f1-851d-1baf5e6aaf43/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::320853c0-f03a-11ee-848f-314e75eb0e80::assets::4672c130-2826-11f1-87e7-fd43b